a7318ff5-9e47-423c-aa88-05077dfe9470.title: Elena
a7318ff5-9e47-423c-aa88-05077dfe9470.text: Hey get me out of here please!

71ff99ac-0a6f-4216-95c3-ad68d4f6fd05.title: <player>
71ff99ac-0a6f-4216-95c3-ad68d4f6fd05.text: I would do but I don't have a key.

6eb57993-32d1-4089-8515-ebc163ef5271.title: Elena
6eb57993-32d1-4089-8515-ebc163ef5271.text:
I think there may be one around somewhere. I'm sure
I heard them stashing it somewhere.

9095e79d-0bf8-4cde-b9c1-ba9d4cef6712.title: Elena
9095e79d-0bf8-4cde-b9c1-ba9d4cef6712.text: No, I have none of the symptoms.

fdf97450-f233-4cf5-93da-141f33c8d967.title: <player>
fdf97450-f233-4cf5-93da-141f33c8d967.text: Strange, I was told this house was plague infected.

2334cb15-8e6a-4806-995b-e380df7f2fea.title: Elena
2334cb15-8e6a-4806-995b-e380df7f2fea.text: I suppose that was a cover up by the kidnappers.

7f755bd4-aca6-4ed7-9799-e56610c892f7.title: Note
7f755bd4-aca6-4ed7-9799-e56610c892f7.text:
Do you have the key?
Its in a barrel west of the stairs.
